1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,620 --> 00:00:55,540
=Episode 17=

3
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:58,880
I have something for you.

4
00:01:02,079 --> 00:01:03,840
When I was buying masks over there,

5
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:05,280
I found this.

6
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:11,079
It would look great on you.

7
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:13,239
A wand pendant.

8
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:15,719
You think I'm that savage?

9
00:01:16,959 --> 00:01:19,200
This is the Golden Wand
from Bride Snatch to the West!

10
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:23,159
I hope it can watch over you

11
00:01:23,799 --> 00:01:26,519
and turn every misfortune into safety.

12
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:36,359
Your mask

13
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,319
is unique.

14
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,439
It's Zhujiujie.

15
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,519
That's who I want to be.

16
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:47,000
Other girls want to be fairies

17
00:01:47,319 --> 00:01:49,200
to play out a heavenly romance on Qixi

18
00:01:49,719 --> 00:01:51,959
and meet their fated one.

19
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:55,480
But why do you want to become Zhujiujie?

20
00:01:55,959 --> 00:01:57,640
I'm not sure
if I ever mentioned this to you.

21
00:01:58,159 --> 00:01:59,840
I was in an accident

22
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,000
and lost my memory.

23
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,959
I don't remember my mother

24
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,640
or my maid.

25
00:02:05,439 --> 00:02:07,079
When I was bedridden and recovering,

26
00:02:07,719 --> 00:02:08,879
I was in despair.

27
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:11,360
At that time, Bride Snatch to the West
was my only companion.

28
00:02:11,719 --> 00:02:13,120
Though Zhujiujie

29
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:16,240
often talked about
splitting up and giving up,

30
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:18,599
he was actually the most genuine,

31
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,560
the most optimistic.

32
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:23,159
He cried and laughed as he pleased.

33
00:02:23,439 --> 00:02:25,400
He was unruly and wild,
free to be himself.

34
00:02:26,159 --> 00:02:27,439
And still, he made it to the end.

35
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,319
Reading the stories

36
00:02:29,319 --> 00:02:30,719
helped me recover.

37
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,199
And now I'm good.

38
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:37,280
On the surface, you seem cynical,

39
00:02:37,639 --> 00:02:39,800
but in truth, you are the most earnest.

40
00:02:40,319 --> 00:02:41,840
We've only met a few times.

41
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,960
How do you understand me so well?

42
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,479
Knowing a person

43
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,120
isn't about how many times you've met,

44
00:02:51,039 --> 00:02:53,120
but about the distance
between two hearts.

45
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,000
I get you.

46
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,319
I don't think you could.

47
00:02:58,039 --> 00:02:58,960
This thing

48
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:00,919
doesn't happen to everyone.

49
00:03:04,759 --> 00:03:05,680
Actually...

50
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,680
Actually, I...

51
00:03:14,919 --> 00:03:15,479
Hungry?

52
00:03:16,639 --> 00:03:17,120
Come on.

53
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,840
Let's go get some delicacies.

54
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,080
Tell me

55
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,360
where His Majesty is,

56
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:31,840
or

57
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:34,479
I'll find a way to silence you forever.

58
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,280
Your Highness,

59
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:37,240
I would never dare defy
His Majesty's commands!

60
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,000
Say it.

61
00:03:38,439 --> 00:03:39,199
The truth is

62
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:42,000
that His Majesty wanted to
go to the Qixi Festival.

63
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,719
Last night, he ordered me
to splash him with water

64
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,319
from the pond in the Imperial Garden,

65
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,879
saying it was the only way
to deceive you.

66
00:03:50,439 --> 00:03:51,080
Impudent!

67
00:03:51,759 --> 00:03:53,639
How could you indulge him
in such foolishness?

68
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,280
Let's go and find him now!

69
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,479
I feel like Prince Mo

70
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,680
is becoming His Majesty's
surrogate father.

71
00:04:01,940 --> 00:04:04,919
(Yunlai Inn)

72
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:05,560
(Yunlai Inn)
Coming right up!

73
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,439
(Yunlai Inn)
One jin of pupae!

74
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,080
Enjoy your meal!

75
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,319
Young couple,

76
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,199
you look so familiar!

77
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:17,079
We've never been here before.
You must be mistaken.

78
00:04:18,439 --> 00:04:19,279
It just came back to me.

79
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,639
Last time,

80
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:22,240
you were arguing with the eunuch!

81
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,439
You...

82
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:28,279
It's all coming back.

83
00:04:28,399 --> 00:04:30,000
You're that eunuch!

84
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:32,120
Someone's calling you over there.

85
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:33,439
Check it out.

86
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,079
Wishing you happiness!

87
00:04:38,319 --> 00:04:39,160
I bet you've been waiting a while.

88
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,399
Are you hungry?

89
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:43,360
Why do you look so pale?

90
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,639
Your lips are drained of color.

91
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,240
I'm fine.

92
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,199
Just caught a bit of a chill.

93
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:49,360
I'll be fine once I warm up.

94
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,600
Your head is burning up!

95
00:04:53,839 --> 00:04:54,959
We need to see a doctor.

96
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:56,879
I'm fine.

97
00:04:58,079 --> 00:04:59,040
Let me serve you.

98
00:05:05,959 --> 00:05:07,360
Mo Shuo! Mo Shuo!

99
00:05:07,879 --> 00:05:08,519
What happened to him?

100
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,800
He was fine just a moment ago!

101
00:05:10,079 --> 00:05:11,040
Is there a clinic nearby?

102
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:11,959
It's Qixi Festival today.

103
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:13,160
All the clinics around are closed.

104
00:05:13,439 --> 00:05:14,920
Take him to the west quarter now

105
00:05:15,079 --> 00:05:16,240
and see if there's any traveling doctor.

106
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:32,439
Mo Shuo, when are you coming?

107
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:35,319
Didn't you promise
to spend Qixi with me?

108
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,839
I couldn't even buy the sword

109
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,959
I wanted earlier.

110
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,959
If being with someone is impossible,

111
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:06,600
does that mean I'm not allowed to hope?

112
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:09,680
Your Highness.

113
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,439
We haven't found His Majesty.

114
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,319
Didn't you say we should split up
and search for him?

115
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:18,920
(If it weren't for Ling Xiao's
emergency,)

116
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,680
(I would have kept my word.)

117
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,319
(Ke'er,)

118
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:23,839
(I'm sorry.)

119
00:06:24,879 --> 00:06:25,319
Let's go.

120
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,079
Miss, what's going on?

121
00:06:40,199 --> 00:06:41,920
Sir, I noticed you have a medical kit.

122
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,439
Could you save him, please?

123
00:06:45,759 --> 00:06:46,600
What is he to you?

124
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,680
Why do you want to save him?

125
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,600
He is a very important friend of mine.

126
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,360
Miss,

127
00:06:51,759 --> 00:06:53,160
the clinics on the street
are all closed.

128
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:55,399
If you trust me, leave him with me,

129
00:06:55,519 --> 00:06:56,560
and I will cure him.

130
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:59,279
I think he'd worry if he woke up
and didn't see me.

131
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,879
Please come with me.

132
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,160
How is he?

133
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,839
He's fine.

134
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,000
He just needs some rest.

135
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:21,519
Miss,

136
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,600
may I check the wound on your hand?

137
00:07:26,959 --> 00:07:28,759
I'm good, as long as he's fine.

138
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,959
May I have your name, please?

139
00:07:31,319 --> 00:07:32,519
Where is your clinic?

140
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:33,879
I can come to you for medicine.

141
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,000
My name is Mo Shuo.

142
00:07:36,839 --> 00:07:37,800
Mo Shuo?

143
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,279
Which characters are those?

144
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,759
"Mo" as in dark ink,
"Shuo" as in abundant.

145
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:48,480
What a coincidence!

146
00:07:48,879 --> 00:07:50,160
You're both Mo Shuo!

147
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:53,079
Is there some secret

148
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,199
that only I don't know about?

149
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,160
To be honest,

150
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:59,519
this gentleman is my elder brother.

151
00:08:00,639 --> 00:08:02,560
And Mo Shuo is my true name.

152
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:05,720
My brother had his share
of romantic affairs in the past

153
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:08,079
and often used my name as a cover.

154
00:08:08,759 --> 00:08:10,439
Romantic affairs?

155
00:08:11,279 --> 00:08:12,319
Cover?

156
00:08:12,959 --> 00:08:13,839
When he wakes up,

157
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,040
you may ask him yourself.

158
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,160
By the way,

159
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,160
I have a sword here.

160
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:22,040
Please deliver this to Xia Ke'er for me.

161
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:25,079
How do you know Xia Ke'er?

162
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,240
What are you two to each other?

163
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,720
I think

164
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,159
only she can give a proper answer.

165
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,240
Mo Shuo?

166
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:45,759
Why are you here?

167
00:08:46,879 --> 00:08:48,679
If you're looking to cause trouble,

168
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:50,519
I won't let you get away with it.

169
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,200
Ke'er, you've got it wrong.

170
00:08:53,039 --> 00:08:53,799
Ling Xiao is ill.

171
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,279
Take it easy,

172
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:01,399
Ling Xiao hasn't regained his memories.

173
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:04,679
That's good.

174
00:09:06,679 --> 00:09:08,039
But something worse
than Ling Xiao regaining his memory

175
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,759
has happened.

176
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:13,639
To keep his Qixi date with Mu Ruyi,

177
00:09:14,399 --> 00:09:16,120
Ling Xiao spent the night
in the freezing water,

178
00:09:16,279 --> 00:09:17,080
caught a cold,

179
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,919
and fooled me to escape the palace.

180
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:21,000
You mean

181
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:23,120
between them,

182
00:09:25,039 --> 00:09:26,600
the more we try to hide something,

183
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:30,759
the more likely it is to happen?

184
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:33,639
Take your leave now.

185
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,039
Ke'er.

186
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,279
I'm sorry.

187
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,159
Ling Xiao went missing,

188
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,200
so I didn't come to meet you.

189
00:09:45,159 --> 00:09:46,159
Actually...

190
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,440
I hate you.

191
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,879
You're my first hate.

192
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:51,440
We should never
have celebrated Qixi together.

193
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:53,039
We may celebrate the "Enemy Day" later.

194
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,279
I can explain it.

195
00:09:56,399 --> 00:09:57,360
Don't.

196
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,960
You have been rejected.

197
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,039
That night...

198
00:10:00,639 --> 00:10:01,399
Just forget it.

199
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,440
Treat it as an accident.

200
00:10:03,559 --> 00:10:04,759
How could you take this so lightly?

201
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,840
Was everything between us

202
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:07,799
just an accident?

203
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,320
How can you go back on your feelings?

204
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,080
And what about you?

205
00:10:12,559 --> 00:10:14,120
You calculate everything.
Your every move, every choice.

206
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,039
You're always weighing
the pros and cons.

207
00:10:15,519 --> 00:10:16,440
Where have you been today?

208
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:17,960
In your heart,

209
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:20,480
you've already made a choice

210
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,320
between me and Ling Xiao.

211
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:26,240
Ke'er,

212
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:27,960
all I do is for us,

213
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:29,639
so that we can make this work.

214
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:32,440
As long as Mu Ruyi and Ling Xiao
never meet again,

215
00:10:32,559 --> 00:10:33,320
then we can...

216
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:35,080
Mo Shuo!

217
00:10:35,559 --> 00:10:37,360
You will never understand!

218
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,559
You have your destiny,

219
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,679
and I have mine.

220
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:43,600
Leave.

221
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,440
You don't understand either.

222
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,320
My Lady,

223
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,519
do you know who he really is?

224
00:11:11,879 --> 00:11:13,200
You can do anything,

225
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,879
except get close to him again.

226
00:11:16,559 --> 00:11:17,879
All I want is to care for you,

227
00:11:18,879 --> 00:11:20,559
and I don't want you to be hurt again.

228
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,000
Xia Ke'er,

229
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,480
I already know everything.
